CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 6, 1954, pg. 1 reads: "Moving In - Moving Day will come to 118 families within the next month as Belmar Gardens is completed. The scene here will be a common sight as these families shift to their new homes. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Three men, one wearing light colored cap and cardigan sweater, holding legs of table, moving furniture at Belmar Gardens, with second truck inscribed "P.U.C.A- 48865 Ellwood J. Daniels Moving & Hauling, BR. 1-0537"
